videos.description: B.J. Taylor goes coast-to-coast and makes a tough layup for an and-1.
videos.headline: Taylor absorbs contact for and-1 lay-in

videos.description: Tre Scott hustles for the offensive rebound and throws down a nasty putback slam.
videos.headline: Scott rises for putback slam

videos.description: Tacko Fall protects the rim as he comes up with two sick blocks on the same possession.
videos.headline: Tacko comes up with 2 blocks in same possession

videos.description: For the first time in program history UCF  defeats multiple AP-ranked teams in a single season, following its 58-55 win over 20th ranked Cincinnati.
videos.headline: UCF sets school-record in win over Cincinnati
